700887f-a.title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Willett Avenue
700887f-a.text:
E. Gunhill Road, north side, east from Willett Avenue to
White Plains Road, showing the Williamsbridge station of the I.R.f.
subway. The 3-story building, on the left, is at the N.E. corner of
Willett Avenue.
May 12, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
